cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with the performance of deep neural networks. It could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it discusses the behavior of neural networks. Additionally, since the paper focuses on image classification, it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also proposes a modification to existing measures, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, since the paper discusses the correlation between flatness measures and generalization error, it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
